dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_HydroLine_2014.gdb. [River and Stream lines that represent flowlines and cartographic features such as stream centerlines and river banks.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For current data access please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
